            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="o-width wc-50">
        <div class="o-text-field two-columns ">
            <div class="text-container"><p class="a-paragraph is-richtext">As an area manager, Leona holds a key role in
                    creating strategies to achieve our business goals, from sales to customer experience to talent
                    development within our physical stores. Her tasks include training, supporting and inspiring store
                    and café managers and their teams to grow as leaders and act as ambassadors of the brand every day.
                    Leona is also involved in opening new stores in new and existing markets, which means that she helps
                    store and café teams to build a workplace culture that celebrates our brand values. <br></p></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="o-width wc-75">
        <div class="o-width fullWidth--mobile wc-75">
            <div class="o-image-listing cols-2" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px;">
